org.zaproxy.zap.extension.websocket

Class WebSocketChannelDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zaproxy.zap.extension.websocket.WebSocketChannelDTO
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<WebSocketChannelDTO>

    public class WebSocketChannelDTO
extends Object
implements Comparable<WebSocketChannelDTO>
    Data Transfer Object used for displaying WebSocket connection channels. Intended to decouple user interface representation from version specific WebSocketProxy.
